This page demonstrates the <code>mw.neowiki</code> Lua API for accessing NeoWiki structured data from templates and modules.

The examples use [[Module:NeoWikiDemo]], a demo module included with NeoWiki.

== Reading Property Values ==

<code>mw.neowiki.getValue()</code> returns a single scalar value. <code>mw.neowiki.getAll()</code> returns all values as a table.

